<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_dc874723-c14e-47db-a9ce-c02e3a3c9dfd" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="VIC"><sptc>E2P1</sptc><title id="_2e50913c-d412-4be0-81c0-87ea17116033">Design, construction, installation and maintenance</title><archive-num>2019: GP1.1</archive-num><subclause id="_19fcee43-f1c8-4070-b9f1-39f36c67c9d6" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_cb5e9bd7-3f4f-40ff-b42b-acd8575d9c8c">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Mechanical services, or plant and equipment for heating, cooling and/or ventilation must avoid the following:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_e994658d-3081-46cf-9cc9-f6623107db26">Damage to property.</li><li id="_d9f255d2-6037-43e9-8524-ca513eef7fa8"><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1362_2.0.0.xml#_ba5bd5ee-ef5f-41be-b153-43835028cd86" id="_e4d23637-3355-4146-a533-fff95b015f11" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Loss</xref> of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1186_0.6.0.xml#_905252bf-2ff1-43f8-ae81-2949aa116fee" id="_a5f1c774-e3fb-49a9-892a-cb73973a1160" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">amenity</xref> to occupants.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_038e6791-21a1-4e43-b795-b134fc6329b8" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_e9766527-3f18-4aa0-a4d2-9538c443ac10">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Mechanical services, or plant and equipment for heating, cooling and/or ventilation must ensure the following:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_210f3c11-e263-4e3e-afaa-1bf8a0383b49">Efficient use of energy and water.</li><li id="_bd719e53-efac-4efc-af7f-bbfd0a8636e9">Access for maintenance.</li></ol></subclause></clause>